=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; bord=
er-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: so=
lid; background-color: #ccc;">For instance</a>:</p>
<blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">One of the proposals we flag asks =
the Board of Alphabet (GOOG; GOOGL) to address risks from the use of artifi=
cial intelligence. Rather than simply arguing that this will lead to higher=
 returns at Alphabet itself, the proponent argues, =E2=80=9CWe believe that=
 shareholders, many of whom are widely diversified and may feel the impacts=
 of the potential negative externalities of Alphabet=E2=80=99s AI activitie=
s throughout their investment portfolios, would benefit from improved overs=
ight.=E2=80=9D Another asks Shell PLC to align its greenhouse gas emissions=
 targets with the goal of the Paris Agreement, arguing that =E2=80=9C[a] vo=
te for this proposal is warranted by investors who seek to ensure a long-te=
rm future for the Company and to protect the value of their entire investme=
nt portfolios.=E2=80=9D</p></blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I mean it=E2=80=99s probably the case that pow=
erful artificial intelligence will put some companies out of business? Is t=
hat=C2=A0<em>Alphabet=E2=80=99s=C2=A0</em>problem? Not in a traditional sen=
se, but arguably it is Alphabet=E2=80=99s=C2=A0<em>shareholders=E2=80=99=C2=
=A0</em>problem.=C2=A0</p>
